 />\n至於教條與討論區傳統既野 我覺得值得保留既<br />\n但係over就不了<br />\n批鬥呢家野 心智成熟小小既人同埋旁觀者唔會嬲只會笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真心覺得連登低質左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本來捉5p字同殘體字係為左糾正呢種錯誤既風氣<br />\n但依家好似為捉而捉咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後就成個Post都係正字撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打錯字又嘈 某啲字無個口字又捉<br />\n你係咪未撚打過錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家成日入 Post 睇就只係見到堆正字撚<br />\n同埋一堆boycott撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想睇個Post內容都無<br />\n我黎呢到唔係為左睇你捉錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你同小學雞係咁捉人過界有咩分別<br />\n<br />\n捉錯字呢樣野我覺<span style=\"color: red;\">得</span>唔係錯<br />\n但有啲野適量就夠<br />\n根本依家啲會員就過曬火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成班小學雞圍爐咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後講少少野唔啱聽<br />\n就屌人5p仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n還我連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n全中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"377bff60fecd22b98cf90b927f67beea19a4e17c","tid":201533,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T21:21:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無啦啦咁樣騎劫左個post<br />\n搞到騷擾住真心想討論嘅人<br />\n呢啲人真係on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有啲明明前幾頁屌左<br />\n過幾頁又突然間推返上黎話「乜乜乜都冇人屌,連登已死」<br />\n好心呢啲人屌人之前追下p