sets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f1bfd7f31d71c9c4fa4549ea285b7206430cec0","tid":201533,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T21:33:15.000Z","msg":"比負評既係咪都係垃圾車迷？"},{"pid":"7b0c4319fb7b79d2474ca85767f578ee4bdbe722","tid":201533,"uid":66951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T21:35:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主你係連登講呢D野無用，因為連登垃圾居多，我講呢樣野接近收左700個負皮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我就未撚驚過正負評呢d<br />\n至於5p語言<br />\n我係動漫台傾動漫野唔會有呢個騎劫問題<br />\n諗下點解會咁？<br />\n我最歡迎任何人加入一齊討論下</blockquote><br />\n我諗個關鍵係如果大家都係有意識討論一D野，根本唔會為左個錯字而<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正字刑警根本無諗過討論，只係想捉人錯字搵存在感，建立價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c770239a60e6b85efbbef1e522e144cd422f32f2","tid":201533,"uid":45082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T22:08:28.000Z","msg":"我又想知如果係呢個post<br />\n是但一條友將過｢唔｣字<br />\n打咗做個｢吾｣字<br />\n會有咩反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be023ff9f3dada6d186dc651bcbcca4b3f6108e7","tid":201533,"uid":38739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T03:41:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我又想知如果係呢個post<br />\n是但一條友將過｢唔｣字<br />\n打咗做個｢吾｣字<br />\n會有咩反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上面已經有個 &quot;系&quot;"},{"pid":"54f7ecb342e7730c9e8a2ae5c4ee13f262fa24b3","tid":201533,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T03:44:58.000Z","msg":"😩"},{"pid":"8f1aa2308c451fe218acd3863ac8ea1936240fe1","tid":201533,"uid":5921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T03:48:51.000Z","msg":"本末倒置<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcf7dea09a6a5e39a433f723981686ae6381a7e0","tid":201533,"uid":33770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T03:49:19.000Z","msg":"樓